metadata.title: Groundfish Biological Database (Canada)

creators.name: Oceans Canada, Science Branch - Data Analyst

metadata.description:
Parameter
Biological data on individual Groundfish sampled from the commercial and research catches on the coast of B.C.

Measurement Details
Data are collected from commercial, observer, charter and research trip sampling activities. Data include information on individual specimens such as length, sex and age, in conjunction with sampling background data such as species, location and collection methodology.

Pacific Coast of Canada

Other Comments
The Groundfish Biological database is not complete.  At this time, historical Groundfish biological data are being added to the database.

[ A TCODE project ]
